snippet.title: Project SNAQE Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Project SNAQE is an action and precision game inspired by the nostalgic Snake. Collect minerals scattered throughout the map while avoiding monsters, obstacles - and yourself - and see how much can you score in this new spin of a classic.

Project SNAQE is currently under development and is launching for PC on January 4th, 2022.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1725880/Project_SNAQE/



--
